(3665, 'Diflucan 2mg/ml (100ml) i.v. infusion', 'ديفلوكان 2مجم/مل (100 مل)', '', '98', 'Fluconazole', 'Pfizer', 'Unknown', 'غير محدد', '', 'Antifungals.triazoles', '2mg', 'Fluconazole can be administered in the treatment of the following fungal infections[L11043]:
